</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Airship-Zeppelin-LZ-127.svg" class="image" title="airship LZ 127 &quot;Graf Zeppelin&quot;"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cb/Airship-Zeppelin-LZ-127.svg/180px-Airship-Zeppelin-LZ-127.svg.png" width="180" height="64" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
