<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.istrianet.org/istria/navigation/air/lussino-airship.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.istrianet.org/istria/navigation/air/lussino-airship.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.istrianet.org/istria/navigation/air/lussino-airship.htm</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> <i>First World War</i>&#160;— Willmott, H.P.; <a href="/wiki/Dorling_Kindersley" title="Dorling Kindersley">Dorling Kindersley</a>, 2003, Page 192</li>
<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> University of Constance. <a href="http://www.uni-konstanz.de/FuF/Philo/Geschichte/MMAG/MMAG_Zeppelin/Gefahren/gefahren1.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.uni-konstanz.de/FuF/Philo/Geschichte/MMAG/MMAG_Zeppelin/Gefahren/gefahren1.htm" rel="nofollow">Gefahren und Strapazen der Luftschiffeinsätze</a>, upper platform with machine-gun placement and gunners</li>
<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> The figures given total 54. While <a href="/w/index.php?title=A._Whitehouse&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="A. Whitehouse (page does not exist)">A. Whitehouse</a> in <i>The Zeppelin Fighters</i> (1966) gives figures of 5,907 bombs dropped, 528 people killed, 1,156 wounded in 208(!) raids.</li>
</ol>
</div>
